Avidemux is FOSS

to join 2 videos

open video

select the first part

then go to File->Append

select the second part

now be sure that video output and audio output are set

in 'copy'

select as output 'avi muxer'

now go to File->Save

done!


you can do this with .avi or .vob

with .vob files don't click ok when it asks to load all
the videos from a folder (when you have more than 2 video files)
